  <li><a href="http://bit.ly/tensor-charts">TensorCharts</a> - Freemium</li>
</ul>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">TensorCharts has regular discount offers during Black Friday</code></p>

<amp-img itemprop="image" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/atnetcloud/image/upload/v1582614657/atnet/blog_tensorcharts/tensorcharts_vxc3td.jpg" alt="List of Crypto Trading Tools (Free and Freemium)" data-original-width="700px" data-original-height="360px" layout="responsive" width="700px" height="360px">
